<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• لحَا فلانًا:</span> شتَمهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• لحَا الشجرةَ:</span> قَشَرَها.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>